{"tid":2084708,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星展：聲稱話商家認為通過國外法後經濟會好","createTime":"2020-06-29T12:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T12:55:29.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4fe8a4b5be12c7b8ecd8a4fee4eb1b6b3e7317","tid":2084708,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:03:31.000Z","msg":"我唔知佢講香港定Monkeypore會好<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534690-20200629.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534690-20200629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTTnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=d0fb6bb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534690-20200629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8ac64b9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534690-20200629.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n星展集團董事總經理兼財資及市場部總監伍維洪表示，中美問題、新股上市、資金外流等多個因素影響港匯，估計港元與美元仍有利差，而聯繫匯率基本面強，香港有強勁儲備，有關制度不容易破壞，亦未見大規模投機買賣港元。<br />\n<br />\n至於港區國安法，他稱大部份與他傾談的金融市場人士及商家，都認為國安法通過後香港或較安全，生意可能較好，而近期不少壞消息之下股市亦未見很大沽壓，投資者反而傾向在低位買貨。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，如果美國禁止美國公司資金經香港流動，可能短暫對市場有影響，但現時美國仍以經濟利益為主流，相信會盡量不影響在亞洲經濟利益，亦估計不會影響香港的美元結算所自動轉帳系統(RTGS)。<br />\n<br />\n另外，今年業界是財資業務較整體銀行業務做得好，受惠市場波動，客戶要進行對沖等活動，集團首5個月財資市場業務收入按年升30%，下半年若沒有特別事情發生，交易收入或會下跌，但估計大部份銀行財資業務都會有較好表現。"},{"pid":"aa907d01e9fc4877bf1c62a85bf59e14c4783fc6","tid":2084708,"uid":301820,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"當坡狗話：「中共此舉做得好」<br />\n咁即刻香港又衰多幾錢重"},{"pid":"17114480cea97d23e6b83e099a8fa986e2d869c3","tid":2084708,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"理性啲講, 國安法對打擊五大訴求係零作用既"},{"pid":"e6ad3b485165eab26a9b2d8925c48c05d9406182","tid":2084708,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"星展 你支不支持黨安法"},{"pid":"d8ade205b397518317f05adcdd2a8362b63f37bd","tid":2084708,"uid":361893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4YhaOC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4YhaOC.jpg&h=8242f6d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10f2c2e7a7c48676e2bc3aedba28872003fc8209","tid":2084708,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他又提到，如果美國禁止美國公司資金經香港流動，可能短暫對市場有影響，但現時美國仍以經濟利益為主流，相信會盡量不影響在亞洲經濟利益，亦估計不會影響香港的美元結算所自動轉帳系統(RTGS)。</blockquote><br />\n星展祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30a01caf1b7aefcc761da159982ef9f9ef9f9c3","tid":2084708,"uid":2837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"781e784450a1735f2be2fea5f037f795481da3d4","tid":2084708,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa907d01e9fc4877bf1c62a85bf59e14c4783fc6","tid":2084708,"uid":301820,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"當坡狗話：「中共此舉做得好」<br />\n咁即刻香港又衰多幾錢重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:36:28.000Z","msg":"肯定暗爽中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126f8bb1748fc83c0ef87d875ce20954d54219b7","tid":2084708,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDj8hz6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDj8hz6.jpg&h=167b9491&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/29/203625_2ba7352bf1af438f2a5d917afd2ca924.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F29%2F203625_2ba7352bf1af438f2a5d917afd2ca92